title: Shukaku
description: One: Sleeps more than the others; the one with the big dark circles under his eyes, Gaara.

title: Matatabi
description: Two: Burning in flames; with his cat-like voice, Yugito.

title: Isobu
description: Three: Lets the water flow; the fourth Mizukage, Yagura.

title: Son Goku
description: Four: Burns like lava; Together for 40 years, Yonbi and Roshi.

title: Kokuou
description: Five: Always running; the intense power, Han.

title: Saiken
description: Six: Always calm and unhurried; reserved and in a kimono, Utakata.

title: Choumei
description: Seven: A flying insect; the fun Kunoichi, Fuu.

title: Gyuuki
description: Eight: Just what we needed; with crazy rapping skills, Killer Bee.

title: Kurama
description: Nine: Is the number of the great; of Konoha, he is Uzumaki Naruto.
